- We're now going to play split or steal.

00:46:15.104 --> 00:46:17.521
(applauding)

00:46:20.821 --> 00:46:22.730
I know you're the last
two people in the country

00:46:22.730 --> 00:46:25.465
I have to explain this
to, but you have two

00:46:25.465 --> 00:46:27.580
final golden balls.

