If you both choose the steal
ball, you go home with nothing.

00:47:18.760 --> 00:47:20.020
Okay.

00:47:20.020 --> 00:47:23.070
Before I ask you to
choose, I want you to look

00:47:23.070 --> 00:47:25.530
at your two golden balls
and make sure you know

00:47:25.530 --> 00:47:28.300
which is the split ball and
which is the steal ball.

00:47:28.300 --> 00:47:29.907
This is very important.

00:47:29.907 --> 00:47:31.580
Make sure you don't show each other.

00:47:31.580 --> 00:47:32.850
- All right, now they're looking

00:47:32.850 --> 00:47:34.250
at their balls and checking.

00:47:35.524 --> 00:47:37.823
- Before I ask you to choose,

00:47:39.690 --> 00:47:42.730
I think you have some
talking to do to each other.

00:47:42.730 --> 00:47:45.104
- Steven, I just hope there
weren't puppy dog tears

00:47:45.104 --> 00:47:46.840
and they were real tears
and you were genuinely

