50,000.

00:47:52.310 --> 00:47:55.609
I'm just, that's unbelievable.

00:47:55.609 --> 00:47:58.577
I'm very, very happy
to go home with 50,000.

00:47:58.577 --> 00:48:00.190
- You are genuinely going
to split the money with me?

00:48:00.190 --> 00:48:01.750
- If I stole off you every
- She's almost tearing up.

